column5: Just found this site showing a whack load of vintage lures. I have a few old lures myself...   http://www.flickr.com/photos/coop666/sets/72157600169351325/   See how many of the ones listed you have in you tackle box / put away   Gerritt.
I've got a few of these lures myself. A lot of this collection appears to be rather recent - but what would I know, I'm new to the game myself.
Those arent old,Im still using some of them. L M A O  Nice collection Ger.
LOL a lot of them still work. Ya some in the bags or boxes and I have used most. LOL I must be vintage!

Man, that looks like my tackle box! I spotted a "spina ditty", a tiny torpedo, some Bombers I own and well, it looks like they took a pic of my box! Either I'm loaded with the best gear in town, or I need to buy some new stuff! HH

Was going through my Dad's tackle box this weekend and he has soooo, much value in there. I am now wondering how to make them disappear. LOL. Some old stuff he has, have never seen the water, still in original packaging.?  Easton
